snippet.title: Super Robot Wars OG The Moon Dwellers - EN Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming this 2016! First from the Super Robot Wars OG series, Super Robot Wars OG The Mood Dwellers in English for PlayStation 4 - coming to Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Philippines and Indonesia. Join the giants of steel in their fight against hostile invaders!

Disclaimer: In-game dialogue for video illustration purpose. Actual dialogue in game may differ.
